descript.abstract: 1/2 Mile Voluntary Agricultural District Buffer for Gaston County, North Carolina Vector DataPublished on 12.03.2021
descript.purpose: It's purpose is to display a 1/2 mile buffer around parcels that participate in the Voluntary Agricultural District.
descript.supplinf: This buffer represents property within a 1/2 mile of a Gaston County Agricultural Farm. Noises, odors, dust and slow moving vehicles associated with the normal practice of farming may be possible.
